These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, satire, disaster, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, folk, electronic, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, german, italian, japanese
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, train, car, ship
1. the german is the fan of punk##1
2. the italian is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching superhero movies##2
3. the german is the person driving the roller##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the australian##1
6. the person driving the car is the person watching disaster movies##1
7. the fan of folk is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
8. the australian is on the far right##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | superhero   | documentary  | disaster  |
| Music-Genre   | folk    | punk    | hip-hop      | electronic    |
| Nationality   | japanese | german | italian | australian |
| Transport     | ship  | roller       | train    | car     |

