.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, video-games, gardening, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, crime, fantasy, spy
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, snake, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, climbing, rowing, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the hamster is the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person watching spy movies is between the owner of the snake and the person who's sport is skiing##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person watching spy movies and the owner of the hamster##2
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far right##1
8. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping | video-games    | gardening  | fishing    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary      | crime  | spy  | fantasy |
| Pet           | hamster      | snake       | guinea-pig      | hedgehog       |
| Sport         | climbing    | biathlon | rowing | skiing |

