.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, pineapple, grapes, lime
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing, baking, hiking
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, photographer, librarian, videographer
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, bus, quad-bike, car
1. the librarian is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the videographer##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the photographer is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
7. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
8. the person eating radish is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
9. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person eating grapes and the photographer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | pineapple | grapes     | radish   | lime     |
| Hobby       | writing   | rock-climbing   | baking | hiking |
| Job         | electrician   | librarian | videographer       | photographer    |
| Transport   | quad-bike    | bus | jet-ski  | car    |

