.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, musician, security-guard, architect
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, western, drama, thriller
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, chinchilla, horse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, parkour, lacrosse, water-polo
 1. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is the engineer##1
 3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching thriller movies is the owner of the ferret##1
 6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 7. the person watching western movies is the security-guard##1
 8. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 9. the engineer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the musician is between the owner of the mouse and the architect##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | engineer  | architect | musician     | security-guard |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | superhero  | drama | western       |
| Pet           | ferret       | horse    | chinchilla      | mouse           |
| Sport         | golf | parkour   | water-polo   | lacrosse         |

