.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, pumpkin, pineapple, raspberry
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, manager, fisherman, bartender
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, horror, martial-arts, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball, soccer, golf
 1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
 2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far left##1
 3. the fisherman is the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the fisherman is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 6. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 7. the bartender is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 8. the manager is the person watching horror movies##1
 9. the person eating pineapple is between the person who's sport is golf and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | pumpkin         | pineapple         | onion     | raspberry      |
| Job           | fisherman | bartender | accountant    | manager     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy      | martial-arts       | crime    | horror       |
| Sport         | climbing     | soccer       | golf | volleyball |

