 6. the fan of techno is on the far left##1
 7. the musician is on the left of the architect##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
 9. the electrician is between the police-officer and the person who's sport is cricket##2
10. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

