There 4 different types of food: asparagus, mango, artichoke, pepper
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, writing, camping, fishing
4 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, frog, guinea-pig
 1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 2. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 4. the person eating asparagus is the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person eating asparagus and the person eating artichoke##2
 9. the person eating pepper is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is between the person eating asparagus and the person eating artichoke##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | soy-milk    | milk    | fanta      | cola |
| Food       | asparagus        | pepper       | artichoke       | mango     |
| Hobby      | camping | dancing | fishing | writing        |
| Pet        | rabbit       | guinea-pig     | frog         | goat           |

