 5. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the lizard##2
 6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is golf is the person eating avocado##1
 8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is the person driving the airplane##1
10. the person who's sport is swimming is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
